        "evidence": "<p>Addition of selected points, as above.</p>",
        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Risk Class</th>\n<th>Risk</th>\n<th>Point Value</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>Low</td>\n<td>None from Comorbidities, PE findings, or Lab findings</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>II</td>\n<td>Low</td>\n<td>&le;70 points</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>III</td>\n<td>Low</td>\n<td>71-90</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>IV</td>\n<td>Moderate</td>\n<td>91-130</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>V</td>\n<td>High</td>\n<td>&gt;130 total points</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
        "estimation": [
            {
                "name": "Age",
